<HEADLINE>
UW'S NEW COACH HITS TOWN WITH HEFTY TO-DO LIST 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By BUD WITHERS  
 c.1999 Seattle Post-Intelligencer  
