<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-11 10:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6401 &Cx1f; var-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-R-IRAN-DEATHSQUADS-RE     01-11 0973
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-IRAN-DEATHSQUADS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
FRIGHTENING REASSURANCES IN IRAN 
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
