<SLUG> BC-POWERUSER-COLUMN12-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Optimizing a computer can elevate gaming to the surreal
 &HT;    EDs: This is the first in a regular series of columns for
advanced computer users.
 &HT;    By Gerry Yandel
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   I'll never forget the time I saw the light _ literally _ inside
a dungeon.
</P>
