   NETWATCH _ This column will not move tonight. (Katz, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   CYBERSCENE _ What's new on the Web. This week: Food Web sites _
those that do the expected (provide terrific recipes) and the
unexpected (offer little touches that make good use of the unique
advantages offered by a computer and an Internet connection).
(Husted, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   TECHMEDIA _ What the tech magazines are writing about. This
week: Microprose's latest version of ``Civilization,'' one of the
most popular games on CD, ``Civilization II.'' (Haddad, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   MAC-REPORT _ News on Apple and its products. This week: The
annual MacWorld convention. (Haddad, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
MOVED
</P>
