 c.1999 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``Elegy for Iris'' by John Bayley (St. Martin's, $22.95). Scenes
from a 42-year love affair and marriage _ before and after the
onset of Alzheimer's disease. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
