</P>
<P>
   FBN-FALCONS-JAMAL _ Anderson buys offensive lineman big-screen
TVs. They were delivered to locker room on Monday. (Winklejohn,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) 12''
</P>
<P>
   FBN-VIKINGS _ MINNEAPOLIS _ News story from Vikings press
conference. (Bunn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 13.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-FALCONS-NOTES _ Falcons notebook. (Winklejohn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   FBN-VIKINGS-NOTES _ MINNEAPOLIS _ Vikings notebook. (Bunn,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   FBN-BRADLEY-COLUMN _ Mark Bradley writes about the
