<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-11 20:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8618 &Cx1f; taf-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-PATTERNS-FASHION-NYT &LR;      01-11 0657
