   &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; H&AMP;Q  &LR; - The money-making potential of mapping disease-causing genes
drew overflow crowds of investors to two sessions at yesterday's
Hambrecht &AMP; Quist health care conference.
</P>
<P>
