</P>
<P>
   KANSAS-MANHUNT (Overland Park, Kan.) _ Two suspects in a
multistate series of crimes took brief respite at an Overland Park
hotel over the weekend before catching a cab ride that ended in
Wichita. The two are wanted in the killing of a Louisiana car
salesman on Thursday and a bank robbery and the wounding of an Iowa
